Sentencas: Solid Oxide Electrolysis Cell (SOEC) is an efficient green hydrogen production technology, which is a reverse of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell (SOFC).
Titulo: Fabrication of anode supported solid oxide electrolysis cell with the co-tape casting technique and study on co-electrolysis characteristics

Sentencas: In this paper, an anode-supported SOEC produced via multi-layer organic co-tape casting with co-sintering process is investigated for high temperature steam electrolysis, carbon dioxide elec-trolysis, and co-electrolysis.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode supported solid oxide electrolysis cell with the co-tape casting technique and study on co-electrolysis characteristics

Sentencas: SOEC cathode must maintain its electrocatalytic activity in a high temperature and humidity condition.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode supported solid oxide electrolysis cell with the co-tape casting technique and study on co-electrolysis characteristics

Sentencas: La0.75Sr0.25Cr0.5Mn0.5O3-delta (LSCM) is one of the most promising cathode materials because of its superior electrocatalytic ability and redox stability.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode supported solid oxide electrolysis cell with the co-tape casting technique and study on co-electrolysis characteristics

Sentencas: The anode-supported structure of electrolysis cell reduces ohmic resistance obviously and LSCM cathode exhibits good catalytic performance.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode supported solid oxide electrolysis cell with the co-tape casting technique and study on co-electrolysis characteristics

Sentencas: To evaluate the performance of co-electrolysis, a continuous voltage of 1 V is applied for 256 h with 60% H2O and 40% CO2 at 750 degrees C.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode supported solid oxide electrolysis cell with the co-tape casting technique and study on co-electrolysis characteristics

Sentencas: The anode-supported SOEC with LSM((La0.8Sr0.2)0.95Mn0.5O3-delta)/LSM-YSZ(Zr0.92Y0.08O2-delta)/YSZ/LSCM structure has good electrochemical performance and durability under co-electrolysis conditions combined with the distribu-tion relaxation of time analysis of impedance spectra.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode supported solid oxide electrolysis cell with the co-tape casting technique and study on co-electrolysis characteristics
